    "description": "Canara Bank Capital India, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Senior Financial Analyst for our Jaipur operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Canara Bank Capital India:\nCanara Bank Capital India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Monitor financial performance against targets and provide variance analysis\n• Implement and maintain internal controls and audit procedures\n• Prepare annual reports and investor presentations\n• Manage accounts payable and accounts receivable functions\n• Monitor market trends and provide investment recommendations\n• Develop financial models and projections for business planning\n• Manage credit risk assessment and loan appraisal processes\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Financial Reporting\n• Proficiency in Credit Analysis\n• Proficiency in Power BI\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in Forecasting\n• Proficiency in Ind AS\n• Proficiency in QuickBooks\n• Proficiency in Risk Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Referral bonus program\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jaipur, Rajasthan, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Canara Bank Capital India!",
